content:
The common file extensions for images include:

- .jpg or .jpeg (Joint Photographic Experts Group)
- .png (Portable Network Graphics)
- .gif (Graphics Interchange Format)
- .bmp (Bitmap)
- .tif or .tiff (Tagged Image File Format)
- .webp (Web Picture)
- .ico (Icon file)

If you have a specific image or document in mind, feel free to share more details, and I can assist you further!
